d":15926,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/09\/05\/angels-bless-remain-prayer\/","url_meta":{"origin":36908,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Masjid: Angels bless those who wait for prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 5, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe prayer of a man in congregation is twenty-five times better than prayer in his home or shop. When he performs ablution in a good manner and leaves to the mosque only to perform the prayer,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33168,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/11\/imam-rabbana-lakal-hamd\/","url_meta":{"origin":36908,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Salat: What to say when Imam rises in prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 11, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen the Imam says, \u2018Allah heard those who praise him,\u2019 then say, \u2018Our Lord, for you is praise.\u2019 If one\u2019s statement coincides with the statement of the angels, his previous sins will be forgiven.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41209,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/20\/salat-after-fajr-asr\/","url_meta":{"origin":36908,"position"